<HEADLINE> Clinton to Visit Colombia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 4 (Xinhua) -- President Bill Clinton will
make his first visit to Colombia on August 30 to discuss how to
help the country crack down on drug production, the White House
said on Friday.
</P>
<P>
