<HEADLINE> Greece's Annual Inflation Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, August 4 (Xinhua) -- Greece's annual inflation rate
increased to 2.7 percent in July from 2.5 percent in June, the
National Statistics Service (NSS) announced Friday.
</P>
<P>
The inflation rate eased to 2.5 percent in June from 2.9
percent in May, and the figure was 2.1 percent a year ago.
</P>
<P>
