<HEADLINE> Chirac Congratulates British Queen Mum Centenary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, August 4 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
congratulated British Queen Mum on her 100th birthday which falls
on Friday, said the Elysee presidential palace.
