than the total of last week.
</P>
<P>
The market temporarily pushed into negative ground on profit-
taking action, but following interest had never developed with
prices again rising. The market's underlying tone remained bullish
and would post lasting upward movement.
</P>
<P>
On the active players, Health Mineral, the largest mineral
water producer in China, reported a net profit that declined 10.42
percent during the first half of the year, while Chenming Paper
showed a 17.07 increased in net earnings for the half year ended
on June 30. 
</P>
