<HEADLINE> Northwest China's Qinghai Expands Exports </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XINING, August 4 (Xinhua) -- Qinghai Province in northwest
China witnessed a big growth in exports in the first half of this
year, reversing the slowdown over the past few years.
</P>
