72.43 million HK dollars or 37.75 percent less than Thursday's
total, according to Homeway, China's leading on-line financial and
securities information provider.
</P>
<P>
The market failed to reverse the weak note set in the morning,
though it did pare some of its losses towards the close of trading.
Profit-takers started to repatriate gains after three consecutive
sessions of rises.
</P>
