<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 4 (Xinhua) --- Beijing is to host the China-
Africa Cooperation Forum, a ministerial-level meeting from October
10 to 12 this year, Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesman Zhu Bangzao
announced here today on behalf of the Chinese government.
