Cup title last year with two critical singles victories in the 3-2
win against France in Nice.
</P>
<P>
He returned for the opening match of the defense against
Switzerland in February, winning the deciding fifth match to break
a 2-2 deadlock and ensure Australia advance to the quarterfinal
against Germany. 
