to be held during the festival. People will have oppotunities to
look at such rare wild animals as Tibetan antelopes, wild yaks,
wild donkeys, black-neck cranes, the organizer said.
</P>
<P>
Other activities include the beer festival, Tibetan folk
costume show, Tibetan folk-custom show and Tibetan instrumental
performance. 
