<HEADLINE> Results at Italian Grand Prix Diving </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results from
Thursday's FINA Diving Grand Prix meet in Sicily, Italy:
</P>
<P>
