<HEADLINE> Road Accident Kills Seven in Mexico </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, August 4 (Xinhua) -- The collision of a van with a
protection wall in a highway in Mexico's western state of Jalisco
Friday left seven dead and six injured.
</P>
